The blue and white bi-jet screeched through the empty skies of
Cybertron. He had seen something that scared him more than anything for
quite a while, and was not sticking around to find out what that thing
was. Over the horrizon however, three other jets broke loose throught
the clouds. Apeface swerved to aboid hitting Slugslinger, and
transformed, completing his backflip, and landing on a spire in his Ape
mode, clutching it with all hands. "Excellent Slugslinger. Ready to go?"
He asked, making it sound like more of an order. Sluglsinger double back
and swooped by Apeface, "Yeah, I found Quake, but..." he was cut off.
"Quake, he would want to come. I'll go and pick him up, the rest of you
get to base." Apeface ordered. Fine thought SLugslinger, as he continued
his flight. Apeface let go off the spire, and plummetted downard,
transforming back into Jet mode, and roaring towards the bar, using a
radar to detect his old pal Quake.
